                     <interp inst="t17860111-69-off308" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860111-69-off308" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t17860111-69-cd309" type="crimeDate">13th day of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860111-69-off308 t17860111-69-cd309"></join> last, at the parish of <placeName id="t17860111-69-crimeloc310">St. Bennet, otherwise St. Benedict, Paul's-wharf</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t17860111-69-crimeloc310" type="placeName" value="St. Bennet, otherwise St. Benedict, Paul's-wharf"></interp>
